最近，Mosaic搭建了一个能让加利福尼亚州和纽约州居民直接投资太阳能的网络平台<ref>{{cite web
|url= http://gigaom.com/2013/01/08/solar-mosaic-fully-crowd-funds-its-new-solar-projects-in-less-than-24-hours/
|title= Solar Mosaic fully crowd funds its new solar projects in less than 24 hours
