太阳能供热在{{le|主动式太阳能供暖|Active solar heating|主动}}和{{le|被动式太阳能房屋设计|Passive solar building design|被动}}供热建筑以及区域供热系统中早有使用。后者的实例包括加拿大亚伯达省的{{le|德雷克太阳能社区|Drake Landing Solar Community}}以及在丹麦<ref>Holm L. (2012).  [http://www.euroheat.org/Admin/Public/DWSDownload.aspx?File=%2fFiles%2fFiler%2fPresentations%2f20120618-22_EUSEW%2f120619_EUSEW_3+-+Holm+brussel+juni+2012.pdf Long Term Experiences with Solar District Heating in Denmark]{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}. Presentation. European Sustainable Energy Week, Brussels. 18–22 June 2012.</ref>和德国<ref>Pauschinger T. (2012). [http://www.solar-district-heating.eu/LinkClick.aspx?fileticket=4VeN0WSc5Pk%3d&portalid=0 Solar District Heating with Seasonal Thermal Energy Storage in Germany] {{Wayback|url=http://www.solar-district-heating.eu/LinkClick.aspx?fileticket=4VeN0WSc5Pk%3d&portalid=0 |date=20161018073544 }}. Presentation. European Sustainable Energy Week, Brussels. 18–22 June 2012.</ref>的许多区域能源系统。在欧洲有两个太阳能供热项目：“太阳能分区供热”（SDH）<ref>Solar District Heating (SDH) platform [http://www.solar-district-heating.eu website] {{Wayback|url=http://www.solar-district-heating.eu/ |date=20210211125552 }}. Europe.</ref>以及[[國際能源署|國際能源署]]的“太阳能加热与冷却”项目（SHC）<ref>Solar Heating and Cooling programme, of the International Energy Agency. [http://www.iea-shc.org website] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iea-shc.org/ |date=20210220233816 }}.</ref>。

太阳能还未能被广泛应用的原因就在于现在的太阳能技术效率低而且花费高。目前的光伏板只能将所接收阳光的16%转变为电能<ref>{{cite web
|url=http://dspace.bracu.ac.bd/bitstream/handle/10361/732/Solar%20Photovaltic%20Cell%20application.pdf?sequence=1
