{{main|生物质|生物气体}}

生物质（生物质量，{{lang|en|biomass}}），也即来源于活的或者最近活的生物体的生物物质（某种意义上的[[生物材料|生物材料]]）。它通常是指植物或植物衍生物质，此类物质被特别地称作{{le|木质纤维素生物质|lignocellulosic biomass}}<ref name="Biomass Energy Center">[http://www.biomassenergycentre.org.uk/portal/page?_pageid=76,15049&_dad=portal&_schema=PORTAL Biomass Energy Center] {{Wayback|url=http://www.biomassenergycentre.org.uk/portal/page?_pageid=76,15049&_dad=portal&_schema=PORTAL |date=20061008081905 }}. Biomassenergycentre.org.uk. Retrieved on 28 February 2012.</ref>。生物质作为一种能量来源，既可以直接通过燃烧产生热量，也可以间接将其转化为各种形式的[[生物燃料|生物燃料]]。生物质转化为生物燃料的过程，可以由不同的方法实现，大致分为：热的，化学的和生物化学的。木头至今仍然是最大的生物质能源<ref name="online.wsj.com">[http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052702303740704577524822063133842.html Wood-Fired Plants Generate Violations] {{Wayback|url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052702303740704577524822063133842.html |date=20130512024806 }} - Wall Street Journals. Retrieved on 12 April 2012.</ref>；例子包括森林残留物（如枯死的树木或树枝、树桩），庭院修剪物，[[木屑|木屑]]，甚至城市的固体[[垃圾|垃圾]]。另一方面，生物质包括多种植物或动物物质，这些物质可以转化成纤维或其他[[工业化学品|工业化学品]]，包括[[生物燃料|生物燃料]]。工业上，生物质可以通过种植各种植物而得到，包括<ref>{{cite web
|URL=http://www.researchgate.net/publication/242681540_DEVELOPING_A_WILLOW_BIOMASS_CROP_ENTERPRISE_FOR_BIOENERGY_AND_BIOPRODUCTS_IN_THE_UNITED_STATES
|authors=T.A. Volk, L.P. Abrahamson
|title=Developing a Willow Biomass Crop Enterprise for Bioenergy and Bioproducts in the United States
|publisher=North East Regional Biomass Program
|date=January 2000
|accessdate=4 June 2015
|archive-date=2021-02-18
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218234247/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/242681540_DEVELOPING_A_WILLOW_BIOMASS_CROP_ENTERPRISE_FOR_BIOENERGY_AND_BIOPRODUCTS_IN_THE_UNITED_STATES
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>[[芒草|芒草]]、[[柳枝稷|柳枝稷]]、[[麻|麻]]、[[玉米|玉米]]、[[杨属|杨树]]、[[柳树|柳树]]、[[高粱屬|高粱]]、[[甘蔗|甘蔗]]、[[竹子|竹子]]，和各种各样的树种，从[[桉树|桉树]]到[[油棕属|油棕]]（[[棕榈油|棕榈油]]）。

生物质、生物（沼）气和生物燃料，通过燃烧产生热量和动力，也同时会危害环境。污染物如[[硫氧化物|硫氧化物]]（SO<sub>x</sub>），[[氮氧化物|氮氧化物]]（NO<sub>x</sub>），和颗粒物（PM）都会从燃烧中产生。世界卫生组织估计，每年有700万人的过早死亡是由空气污染造成的<ref name="who.int">[http://www.who.int/mediacentre/news/releases/2014/air-pollution/en/ 7 million premature deaths annually linked to air pollution] {{Wayback|url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/news/releases/2014/air-pollution/en/ |date=20140326015904 }} - WHO, 2014-03-25.</ref>，而其中生物质燃烧是一个主要贡献者<ref name="who.int"/><ref>[http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs313/en/ Ambient (outdoor) air quality and health] {{Wayback|url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs313/en/ |date=20160104165807 }} - Fact sheet No. 313, WHO, 2014 March.</ref><ref>[http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs292/en/ Household air pollution and health] {{Wayback|url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs292/en/ |date=20180420035335 }} - Fact Sheet No. 292, WHO, 2014 March.</ref>。如果使用时间跨度够长，生物质的燃烧是零碳排放的，但其他方面则类似化石燃料的燃烧。

===乙醇生物燃料===
乙醇作为北美洲的主要生物燃料形式，许多机构已经在该领域展开研究。政府方面，[[美国农业部|美国农业部]]在美国进行了大量关于[[乙醇|乙醇]]生产的研究，其中大部分都是围绕乙醇生产对国内农产品市场的影响<ref>{{cite web
 |author      = American Coalition for Ethanol
 |url         = http://www.ethanol.org/pdf/contentmgmt/USDA_DOE_biofuels_letter_61208.pdf
 |title       = Responses to Questions from Senator Bingaman
 |publisher   = American Coalition for Ethanol
 |date        = 2008-06-02
 |accessdate  = 2012-04-02
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20111004113944/http://ethanol.org/pdf/contentmgmt/USDA_DOE_biofuels_letter_61208.pdf
 |archivedate = 2011-10-04
}}</ref>。

[[国家可再生能源实验室|国家可再生能源实验室]]对乙醇项目展开了大量研究，尤其是在[[纖維素乙醇|纖維素乙醇]]领域<ref>{{cite web |author=National Renewable Energy Laboratory |url=http://www.nrel.gov/biomass/pdfs/40742.pdf |title=Research Advantages: Cellulosic Ethanol |publisher=National Renewable Energy Laboratory |date=2007-03-02 |accessdate=2012-04-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120125101249/http://www.nrel.gov/biomass/pdfs/40742.pdf |archivedate=2012-01-25 }}</ref>。同传统的以玉米为原料生产的乙醇相比，[[纖維素乙醇|纖維素乙醇]]具有更多优势。因为纤维素乙醇可以从树木、杂草或其他植物身上不可食用的部分中生产，所以不必挪用农作物甚至直接与粮食供给竞争<ref>{{cite journal
| title = Net energy of cellulosic ethanol from switchgrass
| journal = Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America | volume = 105 | issue = 2 | year = 2008 | pages = 464–469 | author = M.R. Schmer, K.P. Vogel, R.B. Mitchell, R.K. Perrin
| doi= 10.1073/pnas.0704767105 | pmid=18180449
}}</ref>。而且，一些研究表明，纤维素乙醇和玉米乙醇相比成本效益更高，经济可持续性更强<ref>{{cite journal
| title = What is (and is not) vital to advancing cellulosic ethanol
| url = https://archive.org/details/sim_trends-in-biotechnology_2007-04_25_4/page/153
| journal = Trends in Biotechnology| volume = 25 | issue = 4 | year = 2007 | pages = 153–157| author = Charles E. Wyman
| doi= 10.1016/j.tibtech.2007.02.009 | pmid=17320227
}}</ref>。[[桑迪亚国家实验室|桑迪亚国家实验室]]则开展了内部纤维素乙醇研究<ref>{{cite web
 |author      = Sandia National Laboratories
 |url         = http://energy.sandia.gov/index.php?page_id=405
 |title       = Biomass
 |publisher   = Sandia National Laboratories
 |accessdate  = 2012-04-17
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20120510101628/http://energy.sandia.gov/index.php?page_id=405
 |archivedate = 2012-05-10
}}</ref>，它同时也是{{le|联合生物能源研究所|Joint BioEnergy Institute}}（JBEI ）的成员之一，该研究所由[[美國能源部|美國能源部]]创建，其目标是开发出纤维素生物燃料<ref>{{cite web
 |author      = Joint BioEnergy Initiative
 |url         = http://www.jbei.org/index.shtml
 |title       = About JBEI
